&lt;p&gt;As part of the AI Foundry within NewRocket’s AI Center of Excellence, this role will help establish the AI Data Readiness layer of the NewRocket Intelligence Platform, enabling scalable AI deployments across enterprise environments including ServiceNow and other operational platforms.&lt;/p&gt;
