&lt;li&gt;Semantic indexing and embeddings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge graphs and ontology frameworks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;AI-ready data pipelines and enrichment layers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Real-time ingestion and contextualization of enterprise data&lt;/li&gt;
