&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NewRocket is seeking a Principal Delivery Architect to lead solution architecture and delivery oversight for a telecommunications client engagement. This individual will serve as the senior technical authority on the engagement, responsible for translating business and operational requirements into a coherent technical roadmap, guiding delivery teams through implementation, and acting as a trusted technical advisor to client stakeholders.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a client-facing, senior-level position requiring deep delivery experience within complex, multi-stream telco environments, strong architectural judgment, and the ability to operate confidently in front of executive and technical audiences alike.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own end-to-end solution architecture across the engagement, ensuring technical decisions align with the client&#39;s business objectives, technical landscape, and long-term roadmap.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the primary architectural point of contact for the client, building trusted relationships with client technical leadership and stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate business requirements into scalable, maintainable architecture and delivery plans, balancing speed, cost, and quality.&lt;/li&gt;
