&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead adoption and OCM streams across &lt;strong&gt;large-scale ServiceNow transformations&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the &lt;strong&gt;primary advisor to client stakeholders&lt;/strong&gt; on adoption strategy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Integrate adoption into &lt;strong&gt;overall program design (not as a downstream activity)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt; AI-First OCM Innovation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and evolve &lt;strong&gt;next-generation OCM methods&lt;/strong&gt;, including:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
